data.description: Townhouse in the gated community "The Riviera by Lennar"! with a pristine patio design and one car garage. This unit offers a lovely outdoor area with an awning, ceiling fan, electrical outlet for TV/Radio, pavers and turf. Other plus are: No back neighbors, deeper lot/patio size, tile flooring downstairs, Zebra window treatment, complete hurricane shutters, washer and dryer closet upstairs, driveway and plenty of guest parking in front of the unit. Clubhouse has a gym and a pool. Close to Publix anchored shopping center and Florida Turnpike expressway. Easy to show!
